      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/varik/{size}/115_2.png",
      "created_at": "2017-01-28T23:00:19.028Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Parashikime jane te miat. Kushtetuten e nderrojne per 20 min kur behet fjale per pazare nen tavoline.<br>\nNuk zbret burisha nga kali, pa e hedh kali ne toke <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/wink.png?v=5\" title=\":wink:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":wink:\"></p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": 18,
